<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ginnan ka gal thila, ka chung van khuo a lang ie,
 Lalpan A siem salem thak a khun;
 Martar haw leh Angel vamte tawh,
 Tuhin Lalchutphah ah ei ngak ui.

[V2]
 Zie chun ei ngak khenlohna ah,
 Hehpih tatte a kimnau ah;
 Lungkham, gimum thuoka maute le,
 Chawldam tanau tih Lalpan a gen.

[V3]
 2. Tuhin kapin khen mah leu hing le I lungdeihteu,
 Mi gen suongmantam sana tuol ah;
 Khen na thu him gen um ta puona,
 Khen lohna ni hung vak zaw tana.

[V4]
 3. Aw, tuhin lei lungkhamna cheng cheng a beih tieng leh,
 Belam no leh Lalchutphah lopi;
 A mi thiengte tawh kumkhawsawt in,
 Zing sawl Aksi guolin vak tan au.

[V5]
 4. Bangtik leh Hukdampa, kumsawt munah nei tun dem?
 Lungkhamna thu him genta loin;
 Khenna, lungkhamna thuoka maute,
 Kipahna tha zaka kikhawm ding.</lyrics>
<title>Lalpa Siem Salem Thak</title>
</song>